----------------------------------- Multi Container App -----------------------------------------------------
- Objective: Deploy a Multi container App
- Task details:
    - Deploy the 'famous-quotes.yaml' file into the 'atlantis' project
    - Use the image "quay.io/redhattraining/famous-quotes:2.1"
    - Use port 8000 for the application
    - Ensure two instances are running
    - Make the application reachabe at http://quotes.apps-crc.testing
    - Use 'quotes' for both labels and resource names
    - set the following environment variables:
           - QUOTES_HOSTNAME = mysql
           - QUOTES_USER = ex280
           - QUOTES_DATABASE = ex280
           - QUOTES_PASSWORD = ex280
- Make sure the application produces an output

oc prkject atlantis
vi famous-quotes.yaml
apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
   name: quotes       ------- Deployment का नाम
   namespace: atalantis
   labels:
      app: quotes          -------- Label एक tag होता है।        इन labels की मदद से Service Pods को ढूँढती है।
spec:
   replicas: 2
   selector: 
      matchLabels:
          app: quotes
   template:
      metadata:
          labels:
             app: quotes
      spec:
        containers:
        - name: quotes
          image: quay.io/redhattraining/famous-quotes:2.1
          ports:
          - containerPort: 8000
          env:
          - name: QUOTES_HOSTNAME
            value: mysql
          - name: QUOTES_USER
            value: ex280
          - name: QUOTES_DATABASE
            value: ex280
          - name: QUOTES_PASSWORD
            value: ex280

------------------------------------
selector:
   matchLabels:
      app: quotes
यह सबसे important हिस्सा है।
Deployment किस Pod को manage करेगा?
उत्तर
जिस Pod का label होगा
app=quotes
------------------------------------
template:
यहीं से Pods बनेंगे।
------------------------------------
Pod Metadata
metadata:
   labels:
      app: quotes
Pod पर label लगाया।
app=quotes
Deployment इसी label से Pod को पहचानता है।
Service भी इसी label से Pod तक पहुँचती है।
------------------------------------
spec:
अब Pod के अंदर क्या होगा।
containers:
Pod में कितने containers होंगे।





oc apply -f famous-quotes.yaml
oc expose deployment quotes --port=8000
service/quotes exposed
oc expose service quotes --hostname=quotes.apps-crc.testing
route.route.openshift.io/quotes exposed

